---
Author: Heraclitus
Source: http://www.heraclitusfragments.com/
Verse: 74
Translator: Charles Kahn
Book: Anaximander and the Origins of Greek Cosmology
Publisher: Hackett Publishing
Copyright: 1994
---
We should not act and speak like 'children of our parents' i.e., in
the way that has been handed down to us.
